Text: ' landslide (in red) for Lincoln in the 1864 election, southern states (brown) and territories (light brown) not in play
   '
k: width2    
Text: '180
   '
k: image2    
Text: 'Abraham_Lincoln_giving_his_second_Inaugural_Address_(4_March_1865).jpg
   '
